{"tid":1766116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冰封1.8萬年「箭頭利齒」遺骸 科學家驚：首遇無法辨識生物","createTime":"2019-12-02T10:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:34:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4561b8aa4128f7b14f06dab62ad9148553d570bb","tid":1766116,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:41:33.000Z","msg":"去年夏季，科學家在俄羅斯西伯利亞永凍土中，挖出了一個冰封長達1萬8000年的生物，由於所在環境溫度極低，其形態保存相當完整，牠擁有一身絨毛，且牙齒、鼻子和鬍鬚都完好無缺，甚至連睫毛都沒有任何受損，這個生物還有待科學家們進行DNA分析比對，目前推測可能是狗或狼的祖先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LkJuUHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkJuUHY.jpg&h=f2f71227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《太陽報》報導，於2018年時，科學家在雅庫茨克（Yakutsk）因迪吉爾卡河（Indigirka River）附近，挖出了一具動物遺骸，牠有著特殊的箭頭狀尖牙，約出生2個月左右後就死亡，被冰封在永凍土中長達1.8萬年，不過牠全身的皮毛都保存的相當完整，模樣彷彿只是睡著了一般。<br />\n <br />\n為了確認這個生物的確切身份，目前已將樣本移送至瑞典古生物學中心（CPG）研究分析，該處擁有全球最大的犬科動物DNA資料庫，不過謝爾蓋（Sergey Fedorov）博士表示，「這是首次遇到無法辨識的狀況」，這結果讓科學家們相當震驚，目前還須更多的基因排序才能辨識該生物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44uJY9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44uJY9O.jpg&h=9f24440b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《西伯利亞時報》報導，有部分科學家推測，這個生物是從狼進化到狗的過渡階段；不過也有專家認為，狗的進化發展可能比狼還要更早。科學家目前將這隻似犬又似狼的生物取名為「多戈爾（Dogor）」，在當地雅庫特語中是「朋友」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7cGLPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7cGLPY.jpg&h=0e6e71a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8c776cc8c2785fd392324f805a5f84c4f3e8084","tid":1766116,"uid":32934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"Death Stranding"},{"pid":"c3e913dc38cc05255b9f333c089353db409de742","tid":1766116,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"狗的祖先？"},{"pid":"f45e914f99fb08285010ed16579ef8bb8125bf8b","tid":1766116,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e913dc38cc05255b9f333c089353db409de742","tid":1766116,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"狗的祖先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad79be3063eb6e6687419ce9e1771ebd5c5877","tid":1766116,"uid":315545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78aa4d13d21e3972c5c37f655ab87a99d8540bf0","tid":1766116,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e76984755b3445b2a78312a514d6ae4f1be592","tid":1766116,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"鼻似狗，但隻手又似貓科...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5401a9d7a3e637dc62a5e6e85119220311d21d47","tid":1766116,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"好可愛，唔知惡唔惡，有冇機會用DNA 復活番<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"1151fdb4bd80f8654ee801585cb9fbf5aa9100e2","tid":1766116,"uid":50506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"挖左出黎 無咁凍 會唔會搞到個屍體腐爛 影響研究？"},{"pid":"74639914a6116ef91a76c5bd06113d0e8692d7a5","tid":1766116,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"黑警唔係想出人頭地咩<br />\n依家俾機會你地<br />\n三萬隻都有長生不老機會<br />\n比你地帶埋家人又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400d1a2b96c198afe0e9da5a771ba7c7d0df7e49","tid":1766116,"uid":104171,"like":0